Tasks for alpha3 release

In priority order...
--------------------
* Add decorator behaviour

Fulfill MustHaveCleanSyntaxForDecoratorsAndFilters acceptance test.

* Add test cases for named parameters

Acceptance test of the form:
$injector->create('Thing', array('a' => 'hello'));

* Add test cases for unnamed parameters

Acceptance test of the form:
$injector->create('Thing', array('hello'));

* Change Singleton to Recycled and write a proper Singleton

Currently creates an instance for each factory. Should really
have a static registry process wide.
